<LP>
   Consolidated TVX Mining Corp. shareholders voted to
approve merging the company with the gold-mining subsidiary
of Inco Ltd.
   The combined company, to be called TVX Gold Corp., will be
62%-owned by Inco, a major nickel producer. Shareholders of
Consolidated TVX, which has interests in gold and silver
mines in Brazil and Chile, will own the remaining 38%.
Consolidated TVX and Inco are based in Toronto.
</LP>
<TEXT>
